were the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">sources</ENAMEX> of the <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">French</ENAMEX> ones (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Lat</ENAMEX> supercilium
and palebra ), but eyelash evidently caused trouble.
