<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">imreasan</TIMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">pupil</ENAMEX> of the eye (probably literally <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">son</ENAMEX> of
contention or the like).

