<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">ablative</ENAMEX> case will have no word for have .  Languages
with the same word for green and blue have
no plural nouns or adjectives.  Languages with
<NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">more than three degrees</NUMEX> of comparison of adjectives
lack words for yes and no .  Languages which do
