(<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1873</TIMEX>), he harassed other self-proclaimed <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">authorities</ENAMEX>,
and, in both books, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">three or four</NUMEX> lines of text
