            <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Hall</ENAMEX>'s authority came from his citations, a mass
so large that desultorily can hardly describe the
intensity of his collecting.  Before the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">OED</ENAMEX> , no one
could have easily located examples to dispute him,
though <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Richardson</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Johnson</ENAMEX> (as revised by <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Todd</ENAMEX> and
