expansively for his voluntary and gratuitous service:
Those who are familiar with the pages of his
<ENAMEX TYPE="LANGUAGE">Modern English</ENAMEX> , his <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">English</ENAMEX> Adjectives in -able
[<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1877</TIMEX>], and his numerous articles and papers on special
