to a <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">later</TIMEX> period.  Squatter, not in the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">American</ENAMEX>
and earliest <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Australian</ENAMEX> sense of one who illegally
occupies land but in the main <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Australian</ENAMEX> sense of
