A group of words reflects the immediate needs of an
isolated settlement seeking self-sufficiency: dairy
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">station</ENAMEX>, farm, farming (restricted to <ENAMEX TYPE="PLANT">crop</ENAMEX>-raising)
farm-<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">station</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">stockholder</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">stock-keeper</ENAMEX>, stockman,
stock <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">owner</ENAMEX>, stock pen , and stock yard .  A group reflects
the use made of local resources.  <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">Two</NUMEX> examples
