<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Philip Gidley King</ENAMEX> wrote in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1794</TIMEX>: The <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Mount Pit</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">Birds</ENAMEX> are as Numerous as ever, Notwithstanding
