            Verbal <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Aggression in The Wizard of Oz</ENAMEX>



            Most <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">North Americans</ENAMEX> and many others worldwide
have watched the movie classic The
<ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Wizard of Oz</ENAMEX> many times, either as <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">children</ENAMEX> or later
with their <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">children</ENAMEX>.  Yet few <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">viewers</ENAMEX> are aware of
the considerable amount of negative language in
