<ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Wizard of Oz</ENAMEX> (<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1900</TIMEX>), is quite different from the film
version, not only in content but also in <ENAMEX TYPE="LANGUAGE">language</ENAMEX>.
For the book's text, I consulted <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">The Wizard of Oz</ENAMEX> ,
