            Most of the aggression and verbal abuse appear
only in the movie but not in the book.  Among the
book's few maledicta --mild and colorless ones at
that--are: You are nothing but a big <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">coward</ENAMEX>! (Dorothey
to the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Lion</ENAMEX>, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">36</NUMEX>), This <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Lion</ENAMEX> is a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">coward</ENAMEX> .  (Scarecrow
