            The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">OCEL</ENAMEX> is, surely, a prodigious undertaking
and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Tom McArthur</ENAMEX>, aided by his <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">wife</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Feri</ENAMEX>, deserves
enormous credit for having produced a well-balanced
